dct_description_sm: Copyright, 1912, by Poole Bros. Chicago ; Canadian Pacific Railway ; Checked C. P. Ry. Lines-Feb, 1919.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Informational text under headings "Ticketing Routes," and "Optional Routes."
Canadian Pacific railways shown in red, others in black.
Shows waterways, cities, state boundaries, steamship routes.
Canadian Pacific Railway emblem at head of title.
